results.name: Cleroux, Barbara
results.notes: In April 2023, applied to return to active status after extended time out of practice;  Active registration (PP) was granted PROVISIONALLY by RegComm with a requirement to complete a period of (direct) supervised practice before full registration would be considered.  Due to personal reasons, Dr. Cleroux had to step away from practice again before that requirement was satisfied and she transferred to NP (as of Jan 1, 2024) and then to Retired (Jan 1, 2025).   The RC "paused the clock" on the terms & conditions of the provisional registration but with the expectation that any application to reactivate would be referred back to them so that an updated decision (with updated T&C if applicable) could be made.
